room_title: Escape room "The Victorian Room" by Hidden Key Escapes in Chicago
room_description: This Victorian-themed room is based on actual events - a perplexing murder that took place in rural England in the late 1800's. This was at a time when detectives just started to become a mainstay of any police department. Your goal is to find all the clues hidden within the room, then use your detective skills to solve the case and correctly identify the murderer. Think you're up for the task?
